Description: Fender 60th Anniversary 2006 Telecaster Deluxe, Bound 3-Color Sunburst w/S-1 switching and Gen 4 Noiseless pickups. This has the same pickups and wiring as the Fender Elite; a $2,000+ guitar! Gorgeous Maple neck with Foil Logo, abalone inlays and the 60th anniversary badge. Comes in a genuine Fender G&G case (pictured) with case candy, neck and saddle Allen Wrench/Hex Keys, hang tags etc... and a beautiful genuine leather Fender strap. Please don’t hesitate to ask any questions or make an offer, thanks for looking.Shipping is $48 anywhere in the lower 48 United States.
